														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2418165">
									

<p>I didn't want to like this, mostly because I headcanon 990 as being a Nobody who was giving a very real warning. Then I remembered that my headcanon for Nobodies includes the fact that the universe rearranges events so that other things caused the results of their actions. So it could have been a Nobody <em>acting through and causing</em> this program. Anyway, with that little bit solved, easy +1.</p>

