<p>I really hope you make more stuff like this in the future because this is amazing.</p>
<p>EDIT: There was one thing that bugged me about this though, and that was the &quot;unnecessary&quot; collapsible about the compatibility between SCP-990 and the nano-EEG nodes. I'm using it in quotes because this is mostly a thing that only seems to annoy me, but I just feel like it's put there for no reason.</p>
<p>This is just meant to be humorous but I spent about two minutes rapidly clicking the additional red text thinking it was a collapsible or an alternate link. Gr8 b8 m8.</p>

